</tr><tr><td><span style="color: darkblue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">link offsite</span></span></td>
<td>[Website](<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">http://website.com</span>)</td>
<td>Website_<br /><br /><span style="color: gray"><em>this must exist elsewhere in the document:</em></span><br />
.. _Website: <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">http://website.com</span></td>
