</tr><tr><th colspan="6"><a name="grouping-alignment" id="grouping-alignment"></a>grouping and alignment</th>
</tr><tr><th></th>
<th><a href="#markdown">markdown</a></th>
<th><a href="#restructured-text">restructured text</a></th>
<th><a href="#mediawiki">mediawiki</a></th>
